title: two hearts, one home
body:
…in which Harry and Y/N start a family.

  • Third book of the FLATMATE trilogy
  • Preview: Every Monday // Chapter: Every Tuesday (Wattpad) and Wednesday (Tumblr) // 12pm GMT.

To encourage more reads on Wattpad, I’ll update the Wattpad book 1 day earlier than on Tumblr. So instead of waiting 2 days after a preview for a new chapter, you can read it the next day on Wattpad.

  1. Honeymoon - Y/N and Harry go to Greece for their honeymoon and run into a couple they hate.
  2. Boss - Y/N deals with more problems at work, and Harry makes a life changing decision.

❥ Drabbles

❥ Playlist:

  1. There You Are - ZAYN
  2. Say You Won’t Let Go - James Arthur
  3. Moon And Back - Alice Kristiansen
  4. She Looks So Perfect - 5 Seconds Of Summer
  5. How Long Will I Love You - Ellie Goulding
  6. Perfect - Ed Sheeran
  7. Thinking Out Loud - Ed Sheeran
  8. Call It What You Want - Taylor Swift
  9. Paris In The Rain - Lauv
  10. Sweater Weather - The Neighbourhood
  11. Yellow - Coldplay
  12. Can’t Help Falling In Love - Haley Reinhart
